eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Are 18-40 years old;
* Were diagnosed with breast or testicular cancer, lymphoma or sarcoma between the ages of 15-39 years old;
* Completed initial cancer treatment within 6 months;
* Are comfortable using the internet;
* Have an active email address OR willing to create one;
* Able to read and speak English.

Exclusion Criteria:

* Have advanced metastatic disease or are receiving palliative end-of-life care;
* Are not willing to be randomized.
